desc: Tina K skin care products were developed by LA-based skin care expert Tina K O'Brien to naturally mimic the health effects which Vitamin D has on the skin. A healthy skincare approach for beautiful, glowing skin.

layout.text:
VITAMIN D:
ARE YOU GETTING ENOUGH?

TINA•K, developed by LA-based skin expert Tina Keshishian, naturally mimics the health effects Vitamin D has on the skin. A proprietary blend of two patented ingredients soak up the sun's good rays, tighten & tone skin and convert harmful UV rays into skin repairing, natural light.
